      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 480,
        "height": 1072,
        "content": "## Automated Shopify Pricing & COGS Calculator with Slack Approval\n\n### How it works\n\n* A scheduled trigger initiates a periodic check of product dependencies and live prices via Google Sheets.\n* The workflow aggregates the data, calculates profit margins using JavaScript, and decides which products require pricing updates.\n* Eligible products have their prices updated on Shopify, followed by conditional Slack notifications confirming the status.\n* A secondary, independent flow listens for Slack commands to process manual product price overrides.\n* This secondary flow parses Slack threads for prices and variant IDs, updates Shopify via HTTP requests, and sends a final confirmation message.\n\n### Setup steps\n\n- [ ] Configure Google Sheets credentials and select the correct spreadsheets for dependencies and prices.\n- [ ] Connect Slack credentials for both triggering events and sending channel messages.\n- [ ] Authenticate the Shopify HTTP Request nodes with valid API keys or Bearer tokens.\n- [ ] Set up global configuration values such as hidden costs and profit margins in the Edit Fields node.\n\n### Customization\n\nAdjust the schedule trigger interval or the JavaScript calculation logic to reflect changes in how your profit margins are determined.\n\n@[youtube](_geRatkc1kU)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
